    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This brown hemp sack is filled with mold spores, soil, and chemical reagents. It can be thrown as a splash weapon with a range increment of 10 feet. Upon breaking open, a sack of sporecrafter's kindness releases russet mold spores in a 5-foot-radius burst and unleashes 1d4+1 vegepygmies in the nearest adjacent squares. The vegepygmies are not under the control of the user, and immediately attack the nearest creatures for 5 rounds, after which they collapse into nonmagical plant matter.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, poison, summon nature's ally III</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Magical Marketplace",
